column16: Marco Scutaro singles on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Brandon Crawford to 2nd.
Angel Pagan flies out to center fielder Colby Rasmus.
Brandon Crawford singles on a line drive to left fielder Emilio Bonifacio.
Guillermo Quiroz called out on strikes.
Gregor Blanco grounds out, second baseman Maicer Izturis to first baseman Adam Lind.
Brett Pill out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Colby Rasmus.   Joaquin Arias scores.
Buster Posey doubles (11) on a fly ball to center fielder Colby Rasmus.   Marco Scutaro scores.    Joaquin Arias to 3rd.
Joaquin Arias singles on a ground ball to shortstop Munenori Kawasaki.  Marco Scutaro advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by shortstop Munenori Kawasaki.
Shane Victorino flies out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Jacoby Ellsbury lines out to center fielder Colby Rasmus.
Will Middlebrooks grounds out, third baseman Brett Lawrie to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Jarrod Saltalamacchia doubles (9) on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Daniel Nava scores.
Daniel Nava doubles (7) on a sharp fly ball to center fielder Colby Rasmus.   Shane Victorino scores.    Dustin Pedroia scores.
